The paper discusses the recent progress in AI due to Deep Learning technology, which is a subfield of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). It also talks about how the brain processes information, which is related to Neural Networks (cs.NE). The paper proposes a new definition of information, which is related to Information Theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses the design philosophy of AI, which is related to Computational Complexity (cs.CC) and Machine Learning (cs.LG).
